room_title: Escape room "Sherlock's Study" by Exodus Escape Room in Los Angeles
room_address: 5642 E La Palma Ave #202, Anaheim, CA 92807
room_description: Do you have the detective prowess of Sherlock Holmes to escape the room? Sherlock Holmes was famous for his investigative skills. What appears to others as chaos, however, is to Holmes a wealth of useful information. Join forces with Holmes to bring down a fierce adversary who threatens all of London.
